==English==

===Adjective===
'''offensive'''

# Causing [[offense]].
#: ''Most [[feminists]] find [[pornography]] offensive.''
# (''team sports'') Having to do with play directed at scoring.
#: ''The offensive coordinator is responsible for ordering all [[rushing]] plays.''

